        <div class="container-fluid">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Six Sigma Green Belt Certification FAQs</h2>
            <div class="course-cert-faq-summary">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-sm-70">
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="lssgb-training-1">
                            <h3>LSSGB Training</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-1">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-1">1. What is Lean Six Sigma Green Belt training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The Lean Six Sigma Green Belt training is a program that gives you knowledge of all the Six Sigma tools and techniques under the Green Belt level, as per the International Association for Six Sigma Certification (IASSC).&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-2">2. How long will it take for me to complete the LSSGB Curriculum?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The LSSGB curriculum is quite detailed, as it covers all the topics to help you understand and implement advanced analysis. You will also learn how to prevent quality defects. So, it may take you a few months to completely understand the curriculum.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-3">3. Why should I choose KnowledgeHut for LSSGB over other courses?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You should choose KnowledgeHut for LSSGB due to several reasons. Our course curriculum has been designed in a phased manner to help you grasp concepts better, from world-class trainers. You will also be mentored by industry experts and given several resources to help you learn.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-4">4. What practical skills can I expect to have after completing this course?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The <b>Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification</b> helps you achieve the following practical skills: </p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>Problem-solving skills </li>
                                                <li>Leadership skills&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Business process understanding&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Change management&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Mentoring skills&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Interpersonal skills&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Statistical skills&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Financial management skills&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Analytical skills</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-5">5. How does a Green Belt certification help me?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The intense competition in the markets require organizations to ensure that their processes are optimized and are there is maximum gain with minimum wastage. Six Sigma is a meticulous, planned approach of interventions and problem resolution that helps identify such processes that are not performing as required and suggests improvements for the same. Six Sigma Green Belts are important members of the Six Sigma team as they assist in monitoring and evaluating work progress and process enhancements. The Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification is a reflection of the holder’s grasp of the Six Sigma concepts and ability to apply the same for organizational benefit.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-6">6. Who is the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course for?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>This online Six Sigma Green belt certification course is best suited for:</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>IT Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>IT Analysts&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>HR Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Team Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Project Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Change Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Finance Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Program Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Improvement Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Quality System Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Operational Line Managers&nbsp;</li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-7">7. What are the prerequisites for the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-7" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>There are no prerequisites for attending this Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification. <br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-1-8">8. What next after Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-1-8" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-1">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The Six Sigma certifications are a process of continuous improvement. After achieving the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt certification, you can try for the Black Belt certification.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="lssgb-certification-2">
                            <h3>LSSGB Certification</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-2">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-1">1. What is Lean Six Sigma Green Belt?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Lean Six Sigma Green Belts are professionals who have been trained in the Six Sigma Green Belt training. They can understand the full process, and work with Subject Matter Experts (SMEs) to deliver improvements as well.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-2">2. How Long Does It Take to Get a Six Sigma Green Belt?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>This varies from person to person. There is no fixed timeline for this certification. You need to learn the full curriculum under the Six Sigma Green Belt course, take the exam, and pass it. Only then will you be fully and properly certified.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-3">3. What is the difference between Lean Six Sigma Green Belt and Six Sigma Green Belt?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The main difference between Lean Six Sigma Green Belt and Six Sigma green belt is that Lean refers to eliminating wastages, while six sigma is about reducing defects and improving quality.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-4">4. How will I get my Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course completion certificate from KnowledgeHut?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You will receive your Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course completion certificate in an e-mail from KnowledgeHut once you have successfully completed the course.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-5">5. Who provides the Green Belt certification?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Lean Six Sigma certifications are offered by the IASSC in partnership with PEOPLECERT. </p>
                                            <p>This is the first level of the Lean Six Sigma Certification scheme, and more advanced levels include the Lean Six Sigma Black Belt Certification.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-6">6. Can I get Green Belt certified without taking the course?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, you can get the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification without taking the course. The only requirement for certification is to pass the exam.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-7">7. What is the process to get Green Belt certified?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-7" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The following are the Six Sigma Green Belt Certification requirements: </p>
                                            <p><b>Step 1: Get Trained </b></p>
                                            <p>Enrol for an upcoming training program by KnowledgeHut, an accredited training organization (ATO) with PeopleCert®, and attend the 24-hour training. </p>
                                            <p><b>Step 2: Take the IASSC Certified Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Exam™ Exam </b></p>
                                            <p>Take the IASSC Certified Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Exam™ and score a minimum of 70% in this 180-minute multiple choice exam. </p>
                                            <p><b>Step 3: Get Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certified </b></p>
                                            <p>Download the e-certificate. You are now a Lean Six Sigma Green Belt certified professional.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-8">8. Do you provide a course completion certificate?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-8" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, you will receive a course completion certificate on successfully completing the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-9">9. How many times can I retake the exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-9" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>If you do not pass an IASSC Examination on your first try, you may not retake the test within two weeks following the first attempt. A third session cannot be scheduled less than three months after the first. Any future sittings must take place at least three months after the most recent unsuccessful one.</p>
                                            <p>Each IASSC test ticket is good for just one exam attempt. If you don't pass, you'll have to buy another exam voucher if you want to take it again. </p>
                                            <p>Candidates for the ATA application are only given one retake attempt. Candidates who failed both their first exam attempt and their retake can reapply for accreditation six months after submitting their original application, but not earlier. </p>
                                            <p>For more details visit <a href="https://iassc.org/faqs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">https://iassc.org/faqs/</a>.&nbsp;</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-10">10. Will my certificate say ‘Virtual’ if I take the certification online?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-10" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>No, your certificate will not mention that the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training was held online. It will look the same as the in-person certificates. <br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-11">11. Do I need to renew my Green Belt certification?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-11" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt certification has a validity of three years after which you will need to recertify.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-12">12. Is the exam fee included in the course fee?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-12" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>No, the exam fee is not included in the Six Sigma Green Belt course fee. The price of the IASSC Certified Green Belt Exam is not a part of the course fee. For more details visit <a href="https://iassc.org/faqs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">https://iassc.org/faqs/</a>. If you still have any queries regarding the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification cost, do reach out to us on <a href="mailto:support@knowledgehut.com" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">support@knowledgehut.com</a> and we will promptly address them. <br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-13">13. Is there an exam for Six Sigma Green Belt?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-13" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes. To get the Six Sigma Green Belt, you need to pass a 3-hour exam containing 100 multiple-choice questions.&nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-2-14">14. How hard is Six Sigma Green Belt exam?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-2-14" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-2">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The Six Sigma Green Belt is a prized certification, with a detailed curriculum. You will have to answer at least 70% of the 100 MCQs correctly in order to pass. So, it can be pretty hard depending on your preparation.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="lssgb-benefits-3">
                            <h3>LSSGB Benefits</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-3">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-1">1. Is Six Sigma Green Belt Certification worth it?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The Six Sigma Green belt certification cost is $295, which is the cost of the examination. There is no separate certification cost.&nbsp;<br></p>
