                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, of course it does. with the Six Sigma Green Belt certification, you can accelerate your career in Quality Management or even better your skills by pursuing the Black Belt certification.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>
