                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-3-4">4. What is the use of six sigma green belt certification?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-3-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-3">
