                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="lssgb-seus-and-pdus-4">
                            <h3>LSSGB SEUs and PDUs</h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-4">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-1">1. How many PDUs will I be eligible for?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You will get 24 PDUs on completion of this Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-2">2. Where are PDUs applicable?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>PDUs are credits awarded by the <a href="https://www.pmi.org/certifications/certification-resources/maintain/earn-pdus" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Project Management Institute</a>. They recognize your dedication to implementing the Six Sigma processes and eliminating defects and improving overall process quality. PDUs are offered by the PMI®, and every PMI® certification, except the CAPM®, requires you to earn a specific number of PDUs per three-year certification cycle.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-4-3">3. What if I have more questions about SEUs and PDUs?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-4-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-4">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Our <a href="#" target="_blank">blog</a> will help you learn more about how to earn a Scrum Education Unit® (SEU®) from Scrum Alliance®. Get all the information you need to take advantage of SEUs for your professional growth, namely: &nbsp;</p>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>What are SEUs and why you need them &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>How to earn SEUs &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>What types of continuing education opportunities qualify for SEUs &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>How to calculate the value of an SEU for Scrum Alliance certifications &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>How to log SEUs for Scrum Alliance certifications &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>How recent SEUs need to be &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>How to determine whether a previously accumulated SEU can be used for Scrum Alliance certifications &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>List of SEU resources put together by Scrum Alliance &nbsp;</li>
                                                <li>Where you can utilize SEUs you have accumulated </li>
                                            </ul>
                                            <p>For further information about SEUs and PDUs, please reach us at <a href="http://support@knowledgehut.com" target="_blank">support@knowledgehut.com</a>. </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="lssgb-workshop-experience-5">
                            <h3>LSSGB Workshop Experience </h3>
                            <div class="course-cert-faq-content accordion-cards custom-cards" id="faq-accordion-5">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-1">1. What are the modes of training offered?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-1" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The Lean Six Sigma Green Belt workshop at KnowledgeHut is delivered through an immersive learning experience platform, via live and interactive instructor-led training sessions. </p>
                                            <p>Listen, learn, ask questions, and get all your doubts clarified from your instructor, who is an experienced practitioner. This way, you can get yourself the Best Six Sigma Green Belt Training experience possible.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-2">2. How are the workshops structured?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-2" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Our Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training focuses on engaging interaction — we only use lectures to cover the basic terms and concepts. Most class time is dedicated to fun exercises, lively discussions, and team collaboration.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-3">3. Are course materials and workshop instructions provided in advance?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-3" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, your course material will be provided in advance. You will receive an email with a link to set your password a few days in advance of the scheduled course. You will have access to the study plan and all the course material. We want to make your Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training as seamless as possible.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-4">4. What course material will I receive?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-4" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The course material comprises of the course schedule or study plan, workbooks and all relevant assignments, assessments, or case studies. We want to provide you the best resources for your Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Online Training and Certification journey.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-5">5. Can I record the session?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-5" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>The sessions would be auto recorded, subject to permission by PEOPLECERT® and the trainer. Based on the permissions, you would have lifetime access to the video recordings of the sessions as well.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-6">6. Can I use my phone or tab for the training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-6" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>No, you will not yet be able to join the training through phone or tab. Please be prepared to join the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Course Online on your laptop or desktop.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-7">7. What if I lose internet connection during the training?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-7" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>If you get disconnected during the training, you will have the option to re-join within about half an hour. Don’t worry about missing any classes of this Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training Online.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-8">8. Where will the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt workshop be held?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-8" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Our workshops are currently held online and anyone with a stable internet from anywhere across the world can benefit from this to get Green Belt certified. You can check out the schedules <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">here</a>.&nbsp;Choose the Six Sigma Green Belt Certification Course schedule that’s most comfortable for you.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-9">9. How do I join the class?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-9" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>You will receive a registration link from us to your e-mail id. You can set your password, log in and start your immersive learning journey through your Lean 6 Sigma Green Belt Certification.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-10">10. What if I miss a class?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-10" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>If you miss a class, you may access recordings of the sessions, provided PEOPLECERT and the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Educator have permitted recordings. At the beginning of every session, there will also be a 10-12-minute recapitulation of the previous Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Class.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-11">11. Is this a live training, or will I watch pre-recorded videos?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-11" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>This is a live instructor-led training where you will be coached by accredited trainers.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-12">12. What platform do you use for video conferencing?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-12" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>We currently use the Zoom platform for video conferencing and will soon be adding more integrations with WebEx and Microsoft Teams. However, all the sessions and the recordings will be available right from within our learning platform, subject to permission from PEOPLECERT and Lean Six Sigma Green Belt instructor. This is a part of our efforts to deliver the Best Six Sigma Green Belt Training possible to you.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-13">13. Will I have other participants in the class?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-13" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Yes, there will be other participants who will actively participate in the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification remotely. They can attend online training from office, home, or any other suitable place.<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-14">14. How does the 24/7 support work?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-14" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>In case of any queries, our support team is available to you 24/7 via the Help and Support section. You can also reach out to your workshop manager on your workshop group messenger. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-5-15">15. I have some more doubts. How can I get them cleared?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-5-15" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-5">
                                        <div class="card-body editor-content">
                                            <p>Should you have any more questions, please email us on <a href="http://support@knowledgehut.com" target="_blank">support@knowledgehut.com</a> and we will be happy to get back to you. &nbsp;<br></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="cert-and-exam-section" id="lssgb-finance-related-faqs-6">
