                                            <p>To avail scholarships, please get in touch with us at <a href="http://support@knowledgehut.com" target="_blank">support@knowledgehut.com</a>. The team shall send across the forms and instructions to you. Based upon the responses and answers that we receive, our panel of experts take a decision on the Grant. The entire process could take about 7 to 15 days. &nbsp;</p>
