                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-6-9">9. Are there any group discounts?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-6-9" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-6">
