                                            <p>Yes, group discounts are available and apply to groups as small as three (3) participants. The more participants that attend a training course, the greater the discount. By registering in groups, you can typically save up 20% to 30% on the course fee. For more details, please check out <a href="#" target="_blank">upcoming schedules</a>.<br></p>
