        "@context": "http://schema.org",
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity": [{
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is Lean Six Sigma Green Belt training?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The Lean Six Sigma Green Belt training is a program that gives you knowledge of all the Six Sigma tools and techniques under the Green Belt level, as per the International Association for Six Sigma Certification (IASSC).&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How long will it take for me to complete the LSSGB Curriculum?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The LSSGB curriculum is quite detailed, as it covers all the topics to help you understand and implement advanced analysis. You will also learn how to prevent quality defects. So, it may take you a few months to completely understand the curriculum.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Why should I choose KnowledgeHut for LSSGB over other courses?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>You should choose KnowledgeHut for LSSGB due to several reasons. Our course curriculum has been designed in a phased manner to help you grasp concepts better, from world-class trainers. You will also be mentored by industry experts and given several resources to help you learn.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What practical skills can I expect to have after completing this course?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The <b>Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification</b> helps you achieve the following practical skills: </p><ul><li>Problem-solving skills </li><li>Leadership skills&nbsp;</li><li>Business process understanding&nbsp;</li><li>Change management&nbsp;</li><li>Mentoring skills&nbsp;</li><li>Interpersonal skills&nbsp;</li><li>Statistical skills&nbsp;</li><li>Financial management skills&nbsp;</li><li>Analytical skills</li></ul>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How does a Green Belt certification help me?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The intense competition in the markets require organizations to ensure that their processes are optimized and are there is maximum gain with minimum wastage. Six Sigma is a meticulous, planned approach of interventions and problem resolution that helps identify such processes that are not performing as required and suggests improvements for the same. Six Sigma Green Belts are important members of the Six Sigma team as they assist in monitoring and evaluating work progress and process enhancements. The Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification is a reflection of the holder’s grasp of the Six Sigma concepts and ability to apply the same for organizational benefit.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Who is the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course for?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>This online Six Sigma Green belt certification course is best suited for:</p><ul><li>IT Managers&nbsp;</li><li>IT Analysts&nbsp;</li><li>HR Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Team Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Project Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Change Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Finance Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Program Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Improvement Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Quality System Managers&nbsp;</li><li>Operational Line Managers&nbsp;</li></ul>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What are the prerequisites for the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>There are no prerequisites for attending this Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification. <br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What next after Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The Six Sigma certifications are a process of continuous improvement. After achieving the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt certification, you can try for the Black Belt certification.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is Lean Six Sigma Green Belt?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Lean Six Sigma Green Belts are professionals who have been trained in the Six Sigma Green Belt training. They can understand the full process, and work with Subject Matter Experts (SMEs) to deliver improvements as well.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How Long Does It Take to Get a Six Sigma Green Belt?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>This varies from person to person. There is no fixed timeline for this certification. You need to learn the full curriculum under the Six Sigma Green Belt course, take the exam, and pass it. Only then will you be fully and properly certified.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is the difference between Lean Six Sigma Green Belt and Six Sigma Green Belt?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The main difference between Lean Six Sigma Green Belt and Six Sigma green belt is that Lean refers to eliminating wastages, while six sigma is about reducing defects and improving quality.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How will I get my Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course completion certificate from KnowledgeHut?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>You will receive your Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course completion certificate in an e-mail from KnowledgeHut once you have successfully completed the course.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Who provides the Green Belt certification?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Lean Six Sigma certifications are offered by the IASSC in partnership with PEOPLECERT. </p><p>This is the first level of the Lean Six Sigma Certification scheme, and more advanced levels include the Lean Six Sigma Black Belt Certification.</p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I get Green Belt certified without taking the course?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, you can get the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification without taking the course. The only requirement for certification is to pass the exam.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is the process to get Green Belt certified?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The following are the Six Sigma Green Belt Certification requirements: </p><p><b>Step 1: Get Trained   </b></p><p>Enrol for an upcoming training program by KnowledgeHut, an accredited training organization (ATO) with PeopleCert®, and attend the 24-hour training.    </p><p><b>Step 2: Take the IASSC Certified Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Exam™ Exam  </b></p><p>Take the IASSC Certified Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Exam™ and score a minimum of 70% in this 180-minute multiple choice exam.   </p><p><b>Step 3: Get Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certified  </b></p><p>Download the e-certificate. You are now a Lean Six Sigma Green Belt certified professional.</p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Do you provide a course completion certificate?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, you will receive a course completion certificate on successfully completing the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How many times can I retake the exam?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>If you do not pass an IASSC Examination on your first try, you may not retake the test within two weeks following the first attempt. A third session cannot be scheduled less than three months after the first. Any future sittings must take place at least three months after the most recent unsuccessful one.</p><p>Each IASSC test ticket is good for just one exam attempt. If you don't pass, you'll have to buy another exam voucher if you want to take it again. </p><p>Candidates for the ATA application are only given one retake attempt. Candidates who failed both their first exam attempt and their retake can reapply for accreditation six months after submitting their original application, but not earlier. </p><p>For more details visit <a href=\"https://iassc.org/faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://iassc.org/faqs/</a>.&nbsp;</p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Will my certificate say ‘Virtual’ if I take the certification online?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>No, your certificate will not mention that the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training was held online. It will look the same as the in-person certificates.  <br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Do I need to renew my Green Belt certification?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt certification has a validity of three years after which you will need to recertify.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is the exam fee included in the course fee?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>No, the exam fee is not included in the Six Sigma Green Belt course fee. The price of the IASSC Certified Green Belt Exam is not a part of the course fee. For more details visit <a href=\"https://iassc.org/faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://iassc.org/faqs/</a>. If you still have any queries regarding the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification cost, do reach out to us on <a href=\"mailto:support@knowledgehut.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">support@knowledgehut.com</a> and we will promptly address them.  <br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is there an exam for Six Sigma Green Belt?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes. To get the Six Sigma Green Belt, you need to pass a 3-hour exam containing 100 multiple-choice questions.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How hard is Six Sigma Green Belt exam?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The Six Sigma Green Belt is a prized certification, with a detailed curriculum. You will have to answer at least 70% of the 100 MCQs correctly in order to pass. So, it can be pretty hard depending on your preparation.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is Six Sigma Green Belt Certification worth it?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The Six Sigma Green belt certification cost is $295, which is the cost of the examination. There is no separate certification cost.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What can you do with a Six Sigma Green Belt?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>With the Six Sigma Green Belt certification, you can enjoy a rewarding and lucrative career as a quality management and control professional.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Does Six Sigma Green Belt help you get a job?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, of course it does. with the Six Sigma Green Belt certification, you can accelerate your career in Quality Management or even better your skills by pursuing the Black Belt certification.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is the use of six sigma green belt certification?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>You can use your Six Sigma Green Belt Certification to access better career opportunities in Quality Control and Management.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How many PDUs will I be eligible for?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>You will get 24 PDUs on completion of this Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Where are PDUs applicable?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>PDUs are credits awarded by the <a href=\"https://www.pmi.org/certifications/certification-resources/maintain/earn-pdus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Project Management Institute</a>. They recognize your dedication to implementing the Six Sigma processes and eliminating defects and improving overall process quality. PDUs are offered by the PMI®, and every PMI® certification, except the CAPM®, requires you to earn a specific number of PDUs per three-year certification cycle.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What if I have more questions about SEUs and PDUs?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Our <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">blog</a> will help you learn more about how to earn a Scrum Education Unit® (SEU®) from Scrum Alliance®. Get all the information you need to take advantage of SEUs for your professional growth, namely: &nbsp;</p><ul><li>What are SEUs and why you need them &nbsp;</li><li>How to earn SEUs &nbsp;</li><li>What types of continuing education opportunities qualify for SEUs  &nbsp;</li><li>How to calculate the value of an SEU for Scrum Alliance certifications &nbsp;</li><li>How to log SEUs for Scrum Alliance certifications &nbsp;</li><li>How recent SEUs need to be &nbsp;</li><li>How to determine whether a previously accumulated SEU can be used for Scrum Alliance certifications &nbsp;</li><li>List of SEU resources put together by Scrum Alliance  &nbsp;</li><li>Where you can utilize SEUs you have accumulated   </li></ul><p>For further information about SEUs and PDUs, please reach us at <a href=\"http://support@knowledgehut.com\" target=\"_blank\">support@knowledgehut.com</a>. </p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What are the modes of training offered?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The Lean Six Sigma Green Belt workshop at KnowledgeHut is delivered through an immersive learning experience platform, via live and interactive instructor-led training sessions. </p><p>Listen, learn, ask questions, and get all your doubts clarified from your instructor, who is an experienced practitioner. This way, you can get yourself the Best Six Sigma Green Belt Training experience possible.</p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How are the workshops structured?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Our Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training focuses on engaging interaction — we only use lectures to cover the basic terms and concepts. Most class time is dedicated to fun exercises, lively discussions, and team collaboration.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Are course materials and workshop instructions provided in advance?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, your course material will be provided in advance. You will receive an email with a link to set your password a few days in advance of the scheduled course. You will have access to the study plan and all the course material. We want to make your Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training as seamless as possible.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What course material will I receive?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The course material comprises of the course schedule or study plan, workbooks and all relevant assignments, assessments, or case studies. We want to provide you the best resources for your Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Online Training and Certification journey.</p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I record the session?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The sessions would be auto recorded, subject to permission by PEOPLECERT® and the trainer. Based on the permissions, you would have lifetime access to the video recordings of the sessions as well.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I use my phone or tab for the training?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>No, you will not yet be able to join the training through phone or tab. Please be prepared to join the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Course Online on your laptop or desktop.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What if I lose internet connection during the training?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>If you get disconnected during the training, you will have the option to re-join within about half an hour. Don’t worry about missing any classes of this Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Training Online.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Where will the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt workshop be held?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Our workshops are currently held online and anyone with a stable internet from anywhere across the world can benefit from this to get Green Belt certified.  You can check out the schedules <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.&nbsp;Choose the Six Sigma Green Belt Certification Course schedule that’s most comfortable for you.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How do I join the class?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>You will receive a registration link from us to your e-mail id. You can set your password, log in and start your immersive learning journey through your Lean 6 Sigma Green Belt Certification.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What if I miss a class?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>If you miss a class, you may access recordings of the sessions, provided PEOPLECERT and the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Educator have permitted recordings. At the beginning of every session, there will also be a 10-12-minute recapitulation of the previous Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Class.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is this a live training, or will I watch pre-recorded videos?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>This is a live instructor-led training where you will be coached by accredited trainers.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What platform do you use for video conferencing?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>We currently use the Zoom platform for video conferencing and will soon be adding more integrations with WebEx and Microsoft Teams. However, all the sessions and the recordings will be available right from within our learning platform, subject to permission from PEOPLECERT and Lean Six Sigma Green Belt instructor. This is a part of our efforts to deliver the Best Six Sigma Green Belt Training possible to you.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Will I have other participants in the class?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, there will be other participants who will actively participate in the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt Certification remotely.  They can attend online training from office, home, or any other suitable place.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How does the 24/7 support work?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>In case of any queries, our support team is available to you 24/7 via the Help and Support section. You can also reach out to your workshop manager on your workshop group messenger.  &nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "I have some more doubts. How can I get them cleared?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Should you have any more questions, please email us on <a href=\"http://support@knowledgehut.com\" target=\"_blank\">support@knowledgehut.com</a> and we will be happy to get back to you.   &nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What is Six Sigma Green belt certification cost?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>The Six Sigma Green belt certification cost is $295.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is the training for Six Sigma Green Belt Certification cost-efficient?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, absolutely! You will be able to land high-paying jobs in quality control with this global Six Sigma Green Belt certification.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is the exam fee included in the Six Sigma Green Belt course fee?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>No, the Six Sigma Green Belt course fee doesn’t include the exam fee. You’ll have to buy the exam voucher separately.&nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I cancel my enrolment to the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt course? Do I get a refund?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>You can cancel your enrolment and receive refunds in line with our Cancellations and Refunds policy found at <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">#</a>.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is the certification fee inclusive of the course fee?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, the Lean Six Sigma Green Belt certification fee is included in KnowledgeHut’s training fee.  &nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I switch my start date?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, you may switch your start date with prior notice of at least 24 hrs. and subject to availability in the desired batch. <br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is there a money-back guarantee?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, we have a 100% money-back guarantee in line with our <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">100% Satisfaction Guarantee policy</a>. <br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Are there any scholarships available?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, scholarships are available for students and veterans with grants that can vary up to 50% of the course fees.  </p><p>To avail scholarships, please get in touch with us at <a href=\"http://support@knowledgehut.com\" target=\"_blank\">support@knowledgehut.com</a>. The team shall send across the forms and instructions to you. Based upon the responses and answers that we receive, our panel of experts take a decision on the Grant. The entire process could take about 7 to 15 days.   &nbsp;</p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Are there any group discounts?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, group discounts are available and apply to groups as small as three (3) participants. The more participants that attend a training course, the greater the discount. By registering in groups, you can typically save up 20% to 30% on the course fee. For more details, please check out  <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">upcoming schedules</a>.<br></p>"
            }
        }, {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I pay the course fees in instalments?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "<p>Yes, instalment options are available for payment of course fees. To avail the instalment option, please get in touch with us at <a href=\"http://support@knowledgehut.com\" target=\"_blank\">support@knowledgehut.com</a>. The team will explain how the instalments work and provide timelines for your case.  Typically, the number of instalments varies from 2 to 3, but the full amount must be paid before you complete the course. &nbsp;<br></p>"
            }
        }]
    }]
</script>
